    Grocery Stores in Churchgate, Mumbai

    Sometimes called retail stores, grocery stores are established to make available a plethora of food items and household utility products to you. These establishments have made a great amount of progress over the time by also adding on the shelves personal care products. While some of these establishments are known to set on display a range of processed and packaged food, other have a separate counter for fresh vegetables, fruits and ready to eat food items. When shopping at these places you are presented with anextensivechoice of various fast-moving consumer goods (FMCG)products from across brands. Everything that you could need from diary products, juices and other soft drinks to biscuits, tea, sugar and floor cleaners, these stores store them all. You can be sure to find at almost every corner of the city. Payment methods accepted by these shops are both cash and cheque. Please scroll up to find grocery stores in Churchgate, Mumbai.

    Get Groceries Delivered at your Doorstep! Contact the Nearest Grocery Stores in Churchgate, Mumbai!

    There are times when getting out of the house or the busy routine to buy grocery seems next to impossible.     Grocery and Other Staples like dals and pulses, rice and rice products, flour, grains, sugar, salt, oil, ghee, etc.

    Dairy and Beverages including cheese and butter

    Packaged Food Products like biscuits, snacks, ketchup, pasta, ready to cook, sweets, pickle, etc.

    Home and Kitchen Products like detergents, fabric cleaners, utensil cleaners, napkins, kitchen tools, home utility, etc.

    Delivery Services

    Grocery shops Churchgate, Mumbai has, are offering delivery services amidst the coronavirus lockdown. These services are offered during a specific time slot every day. Keeping safety and hygiene at priority all the grocery shops are taking all the necessary measures mentioned in the guidelines by the government as well as WHO to ensure safe grocery home delivery services. Moreover, as a safety measure, many stores are accepting only online payments for home delivery services. Also, note that since the situation is getting critical day by day most grocery shops can deliver only essential food products.

    Delivery Charges

    The delivery charges vary from one grocery store to the other while a majority don’t charge additional delivery charges. It is always best to inquire about the same with the respective Churchgate, Mumbai grocery store.

    Frequently Asked Questions

    1. What are the different grocery items available at supermarkets near me?

    2. Do grocery stores accept bulk orders?

    Yes, all the grocery shops in Mumbai provide fresh and good quality products.

    4. Can defective/expired products be returned?

    In case of any manufacturing defect or quality issue, you can return the product to the store. They may either offer an exchange or refund, depending on the respective store.
